The '''dusky crested flycatcher''' ('''''Elminia nigromitrata''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Stenostiridae]]. It is widespread across the [[Tropical forest|African tropical rainforest]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s and subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]]s.

